    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行立场转为鹰派 准备加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/brazil-central-bank-won-t-hesitate-to-hike-rates-if-appropriate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行表示，随着通胀前景恶化，它将毫不犹豫地提高利率，这标志着在暂停货币宽松周期一个多月后，央行指导方针发生了重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/brazil-central-bank-won-t-hesitate-to-hike-rates-if-appropriate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
