    <item>
      <title>新加坡回应对 17 亿美元安联交易的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/singapore-monetary-authority-defends-1-7-billion-allianz-income-insurance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡部长们回应了对安联集团计划收购收益保险有限公司 (Income Insurance Ltd.) 多数股权的担忧，称该公司将对其承诺负责，并且这笔潜在交易预计不会对该行业的竞争产生不利影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/singapore-monetary-authority-defends-1-7-billion-allianz-income-insurance-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
